, AWS S3, Google GCS, Azure Blob, Aliyun OSS, HWC OBS, TensorFlow Serving, Triton Server, TorchServe","intro_url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TsECBaAvm-g","personas":["SREs","Cloud Architects","Platform Engineers","DevOps Engineer","DevOps practitioners","DevSecOps practitioners"],"release_rate":"Major release every 2 months.","tags":["image acceleration","file distribution","images","OCI","container","artefacts","registry","cloud native","p2p","dragonfly","d7y","nydus"],"use_case":"Provide efficient, stable, securefile distribution and image acceleration based on p2p technology to be the best practice and standard solution in cloud native architectures. It is widely used in the fields of image distribution, file distribution, log distribution, inference model distribution, etc."},"twitter_url":"https://twitter.com/dragonfly_oss"},{"category":"Runtime","homepage_url":"https://cilium.io/","id":"runtime--cloud-native-network--01-超大集群还是多集群-如何定位关键瓶颈-徐俊杰-daocloud-郭奇峰-daocloud-md-cilium","logo":"logos/6b052d96054bbe311b0429d2267d60b92b1c5e6527e6646c0bf2fc06a55e2f43.svg","name":"01-超大集群还是多集群？如何定位关键瓶颈-徐俊杰（DaoCloud），郭奇峰（DaoCloud）.md - Cilium","subcategory":"Cloud Native Network","website":"https://cilium.io/","accepted_at":"2021-10-13","additional_categories":[{"category":"case","subcategory":"true"},{"category":"deep","subcategory":"4"},{"category":"audience","subcategory":"混合"},{"category":"diffcult","subcategory":"4"},{"category":"deployment","subcategory":"3"}],"artwork_url":"https://github.com/cncf/artwork/blob/master/examples/incubating.md#cilium-logos","audits":[{"date":"2023-02-13","type":"security","url":"https://github.com/cilium/cilium.io/blob/main/Security-Reports/CiliumSecurityAudit2022.pdf","vendor":"Ada Logics"},{"date":"2023-02-13","type":"fuzzing","url":"https://github.com/cilium/cilium.io/blob/main/Security-Reports/CiliumFuzzingAudit2022.pdf","vendor":"Ada Logics"}],"clomonitor_name":"cilium","clomonitor_report_summary":"images/clomonitor_cncf_cilium.s